node.text:
Swipe for before 👉🏻
This home was in good shape on the exterior - it just felt a little blah and dull. So, of course, we took care of that! 👊🏻 Those beautiful double steel doors are the most obvious change, but new paint and lighting also really freshened up the look of this home and made it shine. ✨

node.text:
Thanks for all the love on the master bathroom at my #LHIStGeorge reno that I showed you last week 🥰 I wanted to give a special shout out to Bill at @oldebricklighting today. I sent him an idea of a sconce I wanted for this bathroom and asked if he thought he could make it for me. He quickly and graciously said yes, and these sconces are the result of his skill and ingenuity! Aren’t they so pretty? The shade pivots so that you can block as much or as little of the light as you want. Thanks Bill - you did an amazing job! 👏🏻 👏🏻 👏🏻 
.
.
.
.
.

node.text:
I am a huge fan of vintage rugs - how about you? 😍 I’m excited to share that I recently partnered with @revival to create a collection of their gorgeous vintage rugs - Capsule Collection x Kathleen Field 💃💃The collection is live right now on their website - check it out and let me know what you think!The link is in my profile or you can check out today’s story for a swipe up link. This small home office at our #LHItGeorge sports a pretty vintage @revival rug, and I love the character and soul it adds to this room 🥰
.
.
.
